{
	"VersionNumber": 1,
	"ResourceName": "fortinet_log_types",
	"Description": "This is intended to be used as a lookup file providing additional information regarding Fortinet log types. It is used within the Fortinet Kit for dashboards, macros, scheduled searches, alerts, flows, and templates.\n\nfields:\ncategory,subcategory,description\n  - category: this is the log category for the event\n  - subcategory: this is the log subcategory for the event\n  - description: this is more information about the subcategory for the event\n\nReference(s):\n  - Fortinet \n    - https://docs.fortinet.com/document/fortigate/7.6.5/fortios-log-message-reference/160372\n\nUsage: lookup -r fortinet_log_types subtype subcategory (category subcategory description)",
